// DRYFILE: #   Header comment
// DRYFILE-DAG: simple pass xprop FAIL
// DRYFILE-DAG: simple|*|*|pass

// DRYDIFF: --- {{.*}}
// DRYDIFF: +++ {{.*}}
// DRYDIFF-DAG: -simple pass xprop FAIL
// DRYDIFF-DAG: +simple|pass|xprop|fail

