// APPLYFILE: simple|*|*|pass
// APPLYFILE: #   Header comment
// APPLYFILE: simple|pass|xprop|fail
// APPLYFILE-NOT: simple pass xprop FAIL

// APPLYDIFF: --- {{.*}}
